A N A C T
RELATING TO COURTS AND CIVIL PROCEDURE -- COURTS -- FAMILY COURT
Introduced By: Senator David P. Tikoian
Date Introduced: June 06, 2025
Referred To: Senate Housing & Municipal Government
It is enacted by the General Assembly as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Chapter 8-10 of the General Laws entitled "Family Court" is hereby amended
2 by adding thereto the following section:
3 8-10-23.5. Smithfield juvenile hearing board.
4 The town of Smithfield shall have the authority to create a juvenile hearing board subject
5 to the provisions of § 8-10-23.1, notwithstanding the requirements of the town’s regulations, charter
6 or ordinances.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall take effect upon passage.
